title: Jake Paul trolling Floyd Mayweather during the Logan Paul fight! #shorts
author: Omar Raja - ESPN
description:
I had all access at the Logan Paul vs. Floyd Mayweather boxing match and Jake Paul kept talking trash to Floyd Mayweather during the fight. 

Check out my TikTok which has a ton of behind the scenes at different sports events: 
https://www.tiktok.com/@omar

Also check out my Instagram for a sneak peak of all my sports content:
www.instagram.com/Omar
